<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="4" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[401,1802,949,1565]" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">
This large grasshopper, described from a single male from 
<collectingCountry box="[1542,1650,1421,1463]" name="Guam" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">Guam</collectingCountry>
, has not been recorded elsewhere. It was rather common in 1936, often occurring on trees or bushes, rather than on grass.
</paragraph>
